'''牛津大學佛教研究中心'''（{{lang-en|'''Oxford Centre for Buddhist Studies'''}}，縮寫：'''OCBS'''）是[[博登梵語教授|博登梵語教授]][[理查德·貢布里希|理查德·貢布里希]]在2004年創建的研究中心，是[[牛津大學|牛津大學]][[Recognised_Independent_Centre|已認可的獨立中心]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/media/news_stories/2006/061013.html |title=First endowed Professorship in Buddhist Studies in the UK is established at Oxford - University of Oxford |publisher=Ox.ac.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-10-09 |archive-date=2012-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929211920/http://www.ox.ac.uk/media/news_stories/2006/061013.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

該中心主要研究[[佛教|佛教]]，與牛津大學的東方研究系以及人類學、神學系有聯繫。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.orinst.ox.ac.uk/isa/buddhist/index.html |title=Buddhist Studies at Oxford - South and Inner Asia - Faculty of Oriental Studies - University of Oxford |publisher=Orinst.ox.ac.uk |date=2011-11-02 |accessdate=2012-10-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019002942/http://www.orinst.ox.ac.uk/isa/buddhist/index.html |archivedate=2012-10-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theology.ox.ac.uk/37/oxford-centre-for-buddhist-studies-lecture-series.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-03-05  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723150829/http://www.theology.ox.ac.uk/37/oxford-centre-for-buddhist-studies-lecture-series.html |archivedate=2011-07-23 }}</ref>

該研究中心每年都舉辦系列講座和研討會。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/2008-9/weekly/300409/lecs.htm#26Ref |title=Oxford University Gazette, 30 April 2009: Lectures |publisher=Ox.ac.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-10-09 |archive-date=2018-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227090648/https://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/2008-9/weekly/300409/lecs.htm#26Ref |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.balliol.ox.ac.uk/news/2006/october/professorship-of-buddhist-studies-established |title=Professorship of Buddhist Studies established | Balliol College |publisher=Balliol.ox.ac.uk |date= |accessdate=2012-10-09 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812130302/https://www.balliol.ox.ac.uk/news/2006/october/professorship-of-buddhist-studies-established |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

